                  |  means
                  |                     you own this user money
              button.flex-fill.btn.btn-warning.border-0.rounded-5.p-2.text-light.fs-3.fw-semibold.mb-2.me-md-0.me-1
                img.mb-1(src='./images/delete-icon.svg' alt='' width='27')
                |                   Delete Group
              button.flex-fill.btn.btn-primary.border-0.rounded-5.p-2.text-light.fs-3.fw-semibold.mb-2.ms-md-0.ms-1
